Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:39.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}I feel lost,  I feel lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:45.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}書きなぐった手紙のことだけは覚えてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:47.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}It's all true,  it's all true
